text: Today I was relocating from one Public Storage too another and what was suppose to be a quick and simple transition turned out to be this months biggest #@%$& headache, but thanks to Alicia Dominguez ,not only did she save my day she absolutely made my month. So I say again Alicia thank you so very much your help today was Absolutely appreciated....
